<br>
Excuse me but LOL !<br>
I've used 9/18 (Lamy) 10/18 (CBoL) 11/18 (SoZ) <br>
and i can assure you none of these beat Frostry for MTing.<br>
<br>
44/44 is an awesome weapon. Ever tried MTing with it ?<br>
2 swings per week wont help much, 3 misses and no more agro.<br>
<br>
Yes 44/44 will out agro almost anything dropable you can find.<br>
Even SoD / BoC, yes even ultra rare weapons.<br>
But once the procs start going, your game, even with Frosty.<br>
<br>
Remember  MTing has NOTHING to do with Xp &amp; Pure Melee.<br>
When u MT you loose 30% dmg and get stunned often.<br>
The difference between 2 warriors (1 MT 1 Melee) is DPS is almost 2 to 1 ratio.<br>
<br>
The only way to agro when MTing is by procs.<br>
<br>
Why Procs &gt; ALL ? simple they generate agro.<br>
That explains why 95% of warrior tanking Emperor of SSRA<br>
will use 0/16 0/15 weapons with Enraging Blow <br>
And not some 13/20 + 13/20 (shissarbanes) .....<br>
<br>
MTing Agro = 90% Procs , 10% dmg<br>
15/20 +500 Agro is not better than 11/20 +750agro.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   You can not compare : MTing , XP Tanking , Meeleing<br>
<br>
A weapon that owns for MTing (Blade of Carnage) will get<br>
Owned by a SoD when Xping.<br>
<br>
A Weapon that owns for Xping (Septre of Destruction) will get<br>
Owned by 50/45 for Meeleing. </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<br>
My comments may be high end oriented, but i can assure you.<br>
The same things works for mid-lvl.<br>
<br>
With 9/18 9/18 you really think u can out-taunt a roque<br>
with 15/25 and 10/20 Bsing for 400's ? Get a grip with Reality. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5132"/A>
