<br>
Believe me, if I had a direct hate proc weapon, I'd use it when MTing. I don't. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uemiliaeq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EmiliaEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 271<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/15/02 11:56:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3559.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: hmm</span><hr size=1> There is no dropable non procing weapon that will out agro 44/44.<br>
